overview: Join Miss May 1998 Deanna Brooks as she takes you through some of the best moments when celebrities and playmates meet. See William Shatner Rob Schnieder Flava Flav Joe Don Rooney Pharrell Williams and Jenny McCarthy get behind the lens to test their skills with some of the world's most beautiful women including Playmate of the Year 2005 Tiffany Fallon
title: Playboy: Celebrity Photographers 2
